Helios Partners Granted a License to Operate Network of Towers in Tanzania

-- B y   D a v i d   M a l i n g h a   D o y a
-- 
2011-08-05T07:40:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-05/helios-partners-granted-a-license-to-operate-network-of-towers-in-tanzania.html
Helios Investment Partners LLP’s
African unit said it received a license from the Tanzanian
government to operate a network of telecommunications towers in
the country.  Helios Towers Africa bought 1,180 towers from Tigo
Tanzania, a mobile-phone operator, in December, Helios said in
an e-mailed statement today in Dar es Salaam, Tanzania’s
commercial capital.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Malingha Doya in Dar es Salaam at 
 dmalingha@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  